President Barack Obama has been announced as the commencement speaker at Arizona State University, the University of Notre Dame, and the United States Naval Academy in the spring of 2009. He will address graduates, family members, and faculty at Arizona State University on May 13, 2009, the University of Notre Dame on May 17, 2009, and the United States Naval Academy on May 22, 2009. Further details will be provided at a later time.